	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p><add>&#63;</add>&#45;rison with all our precepts of a kindred nature&#44;&#45; for that truth<lb/> is unchanging&#58; they will stand in just and harmonious alliance<lb/> with the inspiration of old&#59; for all true inspiration tends but to<lb/> a common purpose&#44;&#45;a perfect conviction of the duty we owe our<lb/> Maker for his assured justice&#44; mercy and good will towards us.<lb/>  If this inspiration be consistent with that of olden time&#44; it will<lb/> also bring forth more light and knowledge on its great subject&#44;<lb/> since we cannot suppose a revelation to be given but for a<lb/> useful end&#59; and if it should bring no additional influence&#44; it<lb/> could have no important effect.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">What I ask is&#44; to be patiently indulged with attention until</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>the close of a series of articles setting forth the views&#44; in regard to<lb/> <placeName>Israel</placeName> and the world&#44; conferred upon me by spiritual impressions&#44;<lb/> and which I have faithfully endeavoured to maturely investi&#45;<lb/>gate&#44; thoroughly understand and discreetly obey.  If the opportu&#45;<lb/>nity be afforded me&#44; it will confer a lasting obligation&#59; and if<lb/> after an ample exposition of these matters&#44; they should be judged<lb/> erroneous or ill&#45;founded&#44; the result&#44; apparently so lamentable&#44; <add>&#63;</add><lb/> be to me a signal gain&#44; as I shall then stand relieved of the<lb/> momentous accountability of inculcating my views and opinions<lb/> upon my fellow man.</p>
				<p><persName role="author">G. B.</persName></p>
				<p>Private Note</p>
				<p><addressee>Mr. Leeser</addressee>&#44; D<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Sir&#44; If this comm<hi rend="sup">n</hi> will possibly bear insertion&#44; you will greatly o&#45;<lb/>blige me by its admission&#59; &#38; in that case&#44; please send me the N<hi rend="sup">o</hi>. containing it&#44; &#38;<lb/> expect my subscription with the next article.  Yours very faithfully <persName role="author">Geo. Barnard</persName>.</p>
		</body>
